-- Russell Says More Off Broadway Theaters Are Needed (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-09-13T18:55:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-13/russell-says-more-off-broadway-theaters-are-needed-audio-.html
Catherine Russell, one of the 
producers of "The Fantasticks" and one of the stars of "Perfect 
Crime," says she is planning to build 3 more off broadway 
theaters in New York City. She also discusses "The Fantasticks" 
reaching 20,000 performances, and her own record run of 
performances in "Perfect Crime." Russell has been performing in 
the show since 1987. Russell speaks Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  
and Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 12:23
 